    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. I have absolutely babied this car since the day I got it, and it honestly looks like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! It's in pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone new to take it on an adventure. I'm really sad to let it go, but I know you're going to love it just as much as I have. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
